<br>
I was AEing in here with 3 others, 1 chanter, 1 cleric, 1 mage, and myself. Gobs had pretty much low resistances to everything, and were dropping 4-5pp per kill, plus random gems once in a while.<br>
<br>
Exp is decent, and the named that do spawn drop some decent stuff. A named SK way in the back dropped a +7 INT/WIS/CHA +20 HP +30 Mana range item tonight. The mage in our group said he got a decent axe, but didn't mention the stats.<br>
The named also drop alot of quest items, and we've tracked down a couple new quests involved with the revamps. In the Overthere, there is an Ogre that talks about escaping the mines, and wants you to take revenge on the goblins. He wants 3 taskmaster whips and a slinker dagger, or something close to that. Since those gobs were mostly light blue-green to the higher party members, we didn't mess around much with them.<br>
<br>
Basically, it looks like a decent place to AE, or take small groups, and because nothing sees inviso, you can set up pretty much anywhere in the dungeon.<br>
<br>
<br>
Oh, and the mage was talking about the revamped Temple of Droga. He was saying there are some really nasty gobs there now; the bulk are 55-60 and some are 60+. He said the loot was really good, but didn't provide details. Probabaly close to CT type loot though.<br>
Gonna check out Droga sometime this week. I'll post what I find.<br>
<br>
Oh yeah, forgot to mention the casters...<br>
<br>
The place is packed with Shadowknights, wizards, and Necros, so if you've got low resistances, don't bother AEing; you'll die quick. I was getting nailed with 4-5 ice comets/rends before getting in healing range of our cleric. The only thing keeping me alive was my resists (all over 200) and manaskin/manasink. Casters are mean here! <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jarnin>Jarnin</A> at: 6/16/03 12:25 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tombsz>TombSZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 272<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/16/03 6:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Nurga Revamp info</span><hr size=1> I used to AE in Droga for Chardok faction. Used to be alot of fun but I sure was glad when I finally hit ally~ <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tombsz>TombSZ</A> at: 6/16/03 6:11 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=26958.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=26958.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=26958.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=26958.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/theme